snippet.title: RotarySwing.com Golf Instruction
snippet.description:
The official YouTube channel for Rotary Swing Golf Instruction, the #1 online golf instruction website since 2005. The truth about the golf swing, backed by science. New Videos uploaded weekly!

We are specialists in golf swing lag and distance along with all of the fundamentals of the golf swing. Be sure to check in for our weekly PGA Tour swing analysis along with new instructional videos every week. Whether you want to learn how to get more distance fast, or develop a swing like Tiger Woods, we have got you covered. 

We look forward to helping you with your golf game. Good Luck!!
